'''趙承熙'''<ref name="Chinese name1" />（{{lang-ko|조승희}}，{{lang-en|Seung-Hui Cho}}，{{bd|1984年|1月18日|2007年|4月16日|catIdx=Cho Seung-Hui}}）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.npr.org/blogs/talk/2007/04/norris_hall_shooter_identified.html |title=NPR |access-date=2007-04-17 |archive-date=2014-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141208151528/http://www.npr.org/blogs/talk/2007/04/norris_hall_shooter_identified.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>是[[2007年佛吉尼亞理工大學校園槍擊案|2007年弗吉尼亚理工大學校園槍擊案]]的主犯，<ref name=VT>{{Cite web |url=http://198.82.160.236/ |title=VT front page |access-date=2007-04-17 |archive-date=2007-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070417064902/http://198.82.160.236/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = John M. Broder | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2007/04/17/us/17virginia.html?_r=1&hp&oref=slogin | title = Virginia Gunman Identified as a Student | publisher = [[紐約時報|紐約時報]] | accessdate = 2007-04-17 | archive-date = 2021-03-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210321033426/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/04/17/us/17virginia.html?_r=1&hp=&oref=slogin | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="ABC_susp">{{cite news | url = http://abcnews.go.com/US/story?id=3048108 | title = Gunman Identified as Massacre at Virginia Tech Enters Second Day | publisher = [[ABC_News|ABC News]] | accessdate = 2007-04-17}}</ref>[[韓裔美國人|旅美韩国人]]，為該校學生。2007年4月16日，其行兇後[[飲彈|飲彈]][[自盡|自盡]]，其屍體被發現在其他遇難者的遺體中。

== 傳記 ==
趙承熙<ref name="Chinese name1" />生於韓國[[忠清南道|忠清南道]][[安山市|安山市]]，1992年9月，8歲時跟隨父母移民美國[[密歇根州|密歇根州]]的[[底特律|底特律]]。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://today.reuters.com/news/articleinvesting.aspx?type=bondsNews&storyID=2007-04-17T145327Z_01_N17413605_RTRIDST_0_USA-CRIME-SHOOTING-CHO.XML | title = Campus gunman lived in U.S. since 1992 - official | publisher = [[Reuters|Reuters]] | accessdate = 2007-04-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070420140544/http://today.reuters.com/news/articleinvesting.aspx?type=bondsNews&storyID=2007-04-17T145327Z_01_N17413605_RTRIDST_0_USA-CRIME-SHOOTING-CHO.XML | archive-date = 2007-04-20 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>根據[[弗吉尼亚理工学院暨州立大学|維吉尼亞理工學院]]的資料，他是該大學英語專業四年級[[本科|本科]]生。是韓國公民並持有[[綠卡|美國永久居留證]]，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wfaa.com/sharedcontent/dws/news/nation/stories/041807dnnatvatech.1a36bd32.html |title=Gunman's writings raised concerns |access-date=2007-04-17 |archive-date=2008-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080305010128/http://www.wfaa.com/sharedcontent/dws/news/nation/stories/041807dnnatvatech.1a36bd32.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>長住於[[華盛頓|華盛頓大都會地區]]內[[維吉尼亞州|維吉尼亞州]][[費爾法克斯縣|費爾法克斯县]]的縣府直轄地區山特維爾市（Centreville）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/04/17/AR2007041700563.html?hpid=topnews%2F |title=Centreville Student Was Va. Tech Shooter |access-date=2021-05-19 |archive-date=2017-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171006062620/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/04/17/AR2007041700563.html?hpid=topnews%2F |dead-url=no }}</ref>他於2003年畢業于維吉尼亞州費爾法克斯縣的西菲爾特高中（Westfield High School），<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/04/17/us/17cnd-shooter.html |title=Gunman Is Described as Quiet and 'Always by Himself' |access-date=2007-04-17 |archive-date=2020-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216065723/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/04/17/us/17cnd-shooter.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>父母經營一家乾洗店。<ref>A university spokesman described Cho as a "loner", and said university officials were having a hard time finding information about him.[http://www.belleville.com/mld/belleville/news/nation/17091003.htm Gunman identified in Virginia Tech shootings]</ref>一個校園內的韓國人社團指出趙某很少參加[[社團|社團]]活動或和他們交談。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2007/04/18/2007041800037.html |title="범인은 '외톨이'" 조승희 누구인가, retrived from Chosun.com 07-04-17 |access-date=2007-04-17 |archive-date=2013-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004220029/http://news.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2007/04/18/2007041800037.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>在意外發生之前，他已顯示出一些暴力徵狀，反常的行為包括在宿舍寢室內縱火，據稱亦跟蹤騷擾一些女性，相信他有接受相關治療。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,266500,00.html |title=Virginia Tech Police Still Search for Motive After Identifying Shooter |access-date=2007-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070419164814/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,266500,00.html |archive-date=2007-04-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

== 維吉尼亞理工大學慘案 ==
{{Main|2007年維吉尼亞理工大學校園槍擊案}}

據[[美國|美國]][[CNN|CNN電視臺]]報導， 趙承熙於4月16日事發當天曾在宿舍內與兩人發生嚴重爭吵，其間說出「[[太子黨|富家子弟]]」、「[[放蕩|放蕩]]」、「[[欺詐|欺詐]]」等字眼，隨後宿舍內傳出槍聲，兩人身亡。

兩小時後，趙承熙闖入[[維吉尼亞理工大學|維吉尼亞理工大學]]工程系諾理斯教學大樓開槍，造成32人死亡，23人受傷。警方根據從兩支槍上採集的[[指紋|指紋]]與移民案卷認定了兇手[[身分|身分]]。並在兩處[[大樓|大樓]]內採集到[[指紋|指紋]]核對並證實吻合。警方一度怀疑与兇手[[手臂|手臂]]上之紅墨水印記「{{tsl|en|Ismail Ax|Ismail Ax}}」同名的[[同案犯|同犯]]或[[證人|證人]]，但后来证明确实仅有一名兇手。

後來趙承熙被警方包圍於大樓內，兇徒吞槍自殺，脑部中彈。[[維吉尼亞州|弗州]][[警方|警方]]已根据证人供词认定他是此次事件中仅有的「[[縱慾殺手|縱慾殺手]]」（英文：Rampage killer 或 Spree killer）。

== 槍械來源 ==
根據[[美國憲法|美國憲法]][[美國憲法第二修正案|第二修正案]]條文，美國民眾不可剝奪的有擁槍、持槍的權利。每個擁有[[持槍證|持槍證]]的[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]州民均能在本州內方便合法地購買槍支。根據槍械店記錄，赵於2007年3月6日購入一款[[格洛克19|格洛克19]][[9毫米魯格彈|九毫米口径]][[手槍|手槍]]，4月9日又增購一款[[卡尔·瓦尔特运动枪有限公司|瓦爾特]][[瓦爾特P22半自動手槍|P22]][[.22_LR|.22 LR]]（點二二[[英吋|英吋]]）小口徑[[手槍|手槍]]。兩支槍上的序號均被[[銼刀|銼刀]]磨去。

[[美國聯邦調查局|美國聯邦調查局]]相信，兩支[[手槍|手槍]]及[[子彈|槍彈]]均是通過合法途徑，於弗吉尼亚的槍店中購買，根據該州法律，州民每個月只能購槍一枝（或一挺）。
